    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/e15f8ac7d63329119cb803b66c0c60af.avif?t=1683351074\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/4a72b2cf1e74974554ef81a7ef7a7436.poster.avif?t=1683351074\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/4a72b2cf1e74974554ef81a7ef7a7436.webm?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/4a72b2cf1e74974554ef81a7ef7a7436.mp4?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>illum welcomes you to a mystical 3D third-person adventure game, where you embark on a quest to illuminate a dormant kingdom using the power of light.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/acb972dc9d86d6c955842a6fa91e7bd9.avif?t=1683351074\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AWAKEN THE SLEEPING KINGDOM</h2>Form heartwarming bonds with your light friend as you journey together to connect light gems and awaken the slumbering world of Illum.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/b8ed79eedc26d7d10147d2c9fd97c3f0.poster.avif?t=1683351074\" width=598 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/b8ed79eedc26d7d10147d2c9fd97c3f0.webm?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/b8ed79eedc26d7d10147d2c9fd97c3f0.mp4?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A POETIC, EXPANSIVE WORLD</h2>Discover the beauty and narratives embedded in Illum's atmospheric world, as you unravel its secrets of the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIENCE A VISUALLY STUNNING AND EMOTIONAL JOURNEY</h2>Delve into an immersive and poignant adventure that weaves together striking visuals, immersive audio, and atmospheric gameplay to create a truly memorable experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/954600ec5e6379c229cb5df10548da55.poster.avif?t=1683351074\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/954600ec5e6379c229cb5df10548da55.webm?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/954600ec5e6379c229cb5df10548da55.mp4?t=1683351074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380860/extras/bf8c4ffa100ef05758924a887aea3fdb.avif?t=1683351074\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Illum was created as part of CTIN 532: Interactive Design and Production I at the University of Southern California by main developers Elsa Liu and Tianyue Gu, with audio by Raphael Almeida, Richard Wang, Eduardo Resende, and Alexander &quot;Gooch&quot; Duong. For more information, please visit our publisher page. To learn more about the USC Games program, the #1 Games Program in the world, check out the USC Games website, linked to the right.",
